{"title":"最动情的部分——写给为泄洪奉献出家园的农民","authors":["张笃德"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":10,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最动情的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写给为泄洪奉献出家园的农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张笃德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在水的映耀下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透厚积的土层和尘封"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越深刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越纯洁的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是最动情的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以想象被汗水涤亮的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及黧黑的脊背和圣洁的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴光辉的农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栖息在抒情的枝蔓上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高歌爱情的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夏天热烈的光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳朴微笑的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被凶蛮的洪水无情地掀倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂泊的痛苦如扭曲的根……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收在秋天之外抽泣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木犁在田畴的异域蒙尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪洋恣肆的波峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民们打涝起溺于水中的歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦亮湿漉漉的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树起倒伏的栅栏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当都市上空传来悠扬的钟声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便顽强地站立起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力抖落了不幸和伤痕……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过生命的洗礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不甘沉沦的农民哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把抗争的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种植进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九一年不驯的河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排涝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉之躯生长成不屈不挠的责任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席卷了大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却使我们真正认识了农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使农民伟大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民在和水的相濡以沫中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完成了思想的鲜亮"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}